Tia Ling is back and fit as ever. This tiny 5'1 Asian is all muscle and determination. Tia loves to fight and with each match her skills increase. Pound for Pound Tia is the most energetic wrestler on the roster.
Ally Ann is a feisty one, with way too much adrenaline. This off the wall bundle of energy will be dangerous once she learns how to control it. She is flexible and willing to take risks. If she sticks with it, one day this bundle of raw power will be a power to recon with.
A great win for the returning Veteran. Jade gives this 19yr old the fucking of her life. After tying her hands behind her back, Jade just abuses the fuck out of the loser.
